message.content: cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.LG. The paper discusses challenges in building a Question Answering (QA) system with a focus on employing structured data, which involves information retrieval (IR), artificial intelligence (AI), database (DB), computational linguistics (CL), and machine learning (LG) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.CL, and cs.LG.
